response.overview: (2 parts of 45 minutes each) Angkor is the largest temple complex in the world and is located in the middle of the jungle of Cambodia. By far the most famous structure within this temple park is the legendary main temple Angkor Wat. Myths and legends surround this majestic structure. Its importance and impressiveness are undisputed. Experience this fascinating mystery of humanity in breathtaking real 3D images and follow in the footsteps of myth and reality. Not only is the monumental beauty of this legendary temple complex presented, but also legendary Khmer battles, which are re-enacted with the help of martial artists!
response.title: Angkor Wat: Land of the Gods
